cs.DC, cs.ET, cs.CV, cs.AR, cs.LG

The paper deals with the layout decomposition problem in triple patterning lithography, which involves graph theory, optimization, and image processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Discrete Mathematics), followed by cs.ET (Electronic Design Automation), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AR (Hardware Architecture), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
